e xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getEntities()</a><p>Returns an array of uniface.Entity objects contained by the current object, or by the main instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oel1665702532918.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getEntity()</a><p>Get the named entity in the specified occurrence or component instance, or the main instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwv1665702534619.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getInstance()</a><p>Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that contains the current object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrj1665702533649.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getName()</a><p>Returns the fully qualified name of the current Uniface JavaScript object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udv1665702533913.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getParent()</a><p>Returns an Uniface JavaScript object that represents the parent of the current object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/med1665702536765.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getProperties()</a><p>Returns the properties of this Uniface data object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hwh1665702536527.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getProperty()</a><p>Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlx1665702533740.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getShortName()</a><p>Returns the unqualified name of the current Uniface JavaScript object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/agg1665702533827.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getType()</a><p>Returns a constant string denoting the object type.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlv1665702534001.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>isEqualTo()</a><p>Indicates whether the current Uniface JavaScript object equals another JavaScript object, meaning that they both represent the same Uniface object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbz1665702536840.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setProperties()</a><p>Sets widget properties for a Uniface data object in JavaScript.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nkl1665702536608.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setProperty()</a><p>Sets the specified widget property to a given value.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530702\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530702\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Common API Functions Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 11, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Common API Functions Javascript in Uniface makes use of several common API functions. Related Links clearProperties() Restores the initial widget properties of the Uniface data object. clearProperty() Restores the initial value of the specified property. getDSPInstance Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that contains the current object. Deprecated. getEntities() Returns an array of uniface.Entity objects contained by the current object, or by the main instance. getEntity() Get the named entity in the specified occurrence or component instance, or the main instance. getInstance() Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that contains the current object. getName() Returns the fully qualified name of the current Uniface JavaScript object. getParent() Returns an Uniface JavaScript object that represents the parent of the current object. getProperties() Returns the properties of this Uniface data object. getProperty() Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object. getShortName() Returns the unqualified name of the current Uniface JavaScript object. getType() Returns a constant string denoting the object type. isEqualTo() Indicates whether the current Uniface JavaScript object equals another JavaScript object, meaning that they both represent the same Uniface object. setProperties() Sets widget properties for a Uniface data object in JavaScript. setProperty() Sets the specified widget property to a given value. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}